room_title: Escape room "The Space Station" by Escape Sacramento in Sacramento
room_description: You are a crew of scavengers in space. You've discovered an abandoned space station orbiting a distant moon. If you're lucky, you'll be able to scavenge this station for its valuable energy crystals. Find the crystals, and while you're at it, also try to find out what happened here. Don't let your oxygen run out, and keep an eye out for danger: You don't want whatever happened to the crew to happen to you, too.
